  "description": "Rice University is a private research university in Houston, Texas. Its public developer footprint centers on the Rice Research Repository (R-3), a DSpace 9.x platform exposing a HAL+JSON REST API and an OAI-PMH metadata interface, plus a Shibboleth/SAML identity provider and a public course schedule.",
